title: #ThrowBackThursday Quiksilver Pro France -  Kelly Slater - E
description:
Winner of the 2012 Quiksilver Pro France, Kelly Slater battled his way through to the final, up against team mate Dane Reynolds after taking out the likes of Joel Parkinson and Adrien Buchan in earlier heats.
In our final #ThrowBackThursday video, Kelly takes us through his fight for last year's title on the beach breaks of France!
